data.description: North Knoxville home with a large front porch on one level with a garage. This home is in a great location that provides easy access to all of Knoxville. Close to Downtown Knoxville and the up-and-coming Happy Holler area. The kitchen is updated with stainless steel appliances, a professional range hood, granite counter tops, and a slate floor. Most of the rooms have 9 ft ceilings which provides a grand and spacious feel throughout. All the bedrooms are large with hardwood floors. The home was recently updated with new windows, siding, lights, HVAC, plumbing fixtures, and doorknobs. It is ready to be moved into and enjoyed. There is also a carport and an oversized 24' x 20' garage. You do not want to miss out on this home.
